OL,3,CWhat are 'Health MOTs' and who will
OL,4,Cget them?
OL,6,FHealth MOTs are to be offered to older
OL,7,Fand frail patients in A&E departments
OL,8,Fto avoid unnecessary hospital
OL,9,Fadmissions.
OL,11,FThe assessments, which will be offered
OL,12,Fto patients over the age of 65 or
OL,13,Fthose with frailty-related conditions,
OL,14,Fare part of a bid to reduce the amount
OL,15,Fof time people spend in hospital or
OL,16,Fwaiting for ambulances to arrive.
OL,18,FNHS England estimates about one
OL,19,Fmillion people over the age of 75 are
OL,20,Fadmitted to hospitals each year, a
OL,21,Ffifth of whom are very frail.
