OL,3,CWhat are 'Health MOTs' and who will
OL,4,Cget them?
OL,6,FThe tests will run throughout the
OL,7,Fwhole week for ten hours a day and
OL,8,Fthey will check the blood pressure,
OL,9,Fheart health, mobility and
OL,10,Fmalnutrition of the patients.
OL,12,FThe approach could be a "lifeline" for
OL,13,Fmany patients, according to NHS
OL,14,FEngland chief executive Amanda
OL,15,FPritchard, and would allow them to be
OL,16,Fassessed and supported more quickly.
