OL,3,CWhat are 'Health MOTs' and who will
OL,4,Cget them?
OL,6,FMs Pritchard added: "While some people
OL,7,Fdo need to be admitted, it isn't
OL,8,Falways the most suitable place for
OL,9,Folder patients' needs, and they can
OL,10,Falso rapidly lose mobility while in
OL,11,Fhospital."
OL,13,FBased on the results, patients will be
OL,14,Freferred to specialist care, such as
OL,15,Ffall services and dementia support.
OL,17,FDr Tim Cooksley, the previous
OL,18,Fpresident of the Society for Acute
OL,19,FMedicine, said: "It is often too late
OL,20,Fonce a patient is already in an
OL,21,Femergency department"
