OL,3,CWhat are 'Health MOTs' and who will
OL,4,Cget them?
OL,6,F"Urgent and emergency care services
OL,7,Fremain under huge pressure and this
OL,8,Fwill not reduce dangerous overcrowding
OL,9,Fwithout addressing other issues
OL,10,Fsimultaneously."
OL,12,FHowever Sir Julian Hartley, chief
OL,13,Fexecutive at NHS Providers, said:
OL,14,F"Half of hospital inpatients aged over
OL,15,F65 are affected by frailty and the
OL,16,Fgrowing number of people with frailty
OL,17,Fwill have a significant impact on
OL,18,Ffuture health and care services.
