OL,6,F"Community health services are
OL,7,Fspearheading innovative care for
OL,8,Fpeople with frailty, supporting them
OL,9,Fto stay well in their own homes, with
OL,10,Fsome trusts already providing front-
OL,11,Fdoor frailty services within
OL,12,Fhospitals."
